HEADWORD: free-range
<hw>free-range</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>permitted to graze or forage
rather than being confined to a feedlot; -- of livestock and domestic
poultry.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> unenclosed.</syn>⟦br⟧
